All Implemented Interfaces:
Loader
public final class PrebakeScriptLoader
extends java.lang.Object
implements Loader

A loader implementation that tries to satisfy load requests based on the BuiltinResourceLoader or a FileVersioner as appropriate, and that keeps track of the versions of files loaded so that NonFileArtifacts can be kept up-to-date.
